UtMatchInfo

Class to contain information about a matcher's comparison results.  Exists to avoid needing to evaluate a test expression multiple times. The results includes a success boolean, mismatch description, and an LRE value.

Variables
success

Did the matcher evaluate correctly?

mismatch

String representing the mismatch

lre

Logarithm of Relative Error (LRE) value for the matcher.  (Can be number or matrix)
